# Laravel Architecture Rules (Advanced)

## Layered Structure
- HTTP Layer → Controllers
- Domain Layer → Services / Actions
- Infrastructure → Repositories
- Support Layer → Helpers, Traits

## Service Pattern (Mandatory)
- Every business logic MUST go into Service class.

Example:
UserService::createUser()

## Action Pattern
- Use Actions for single operations only.

Example:
CreateUserAction, SendEmailAction

## Dependency Injection
- All services must be injected via constructor.